message.entry: Invalid network input. The network input must be a layer graph, a series network, a DAG network or a string specifying a pretrained network.
Input size mismatch. Size of input to this layer {0} is different from the expected input size {1}.
Feature layer is required when the network input is not a pretrained network name.
Anchor box dimension {0} must be smaller than or equal to image size {1}.
Feature layer, {0}, must be followed by either a Max Pooling layer or an Average Pooling layer, when ''ROIMaxPoolingLayer'' is ''replace''.
The last learnable layer for a Faster R-CNN network must be a fullyConnectedLayer or a convolution2dLayer.
ROIOutputSize must either be 'auto' or a two-element vector of positive integers.
